Oh, nakukuha ko na!

727
00:46:29,860 --> 00:46:31,260
Isa, dalawa, tatlo, apat.

728
00:46:31,390 --> 00:46:32,690
Kaliwa, dalawa.

729
00:46:33,230 --> 00:46:36,506
